tellraw @s ["",{"text":"Splatoon in Minecraft 2 - Rollers and Brushes","color":"green"},{"text":"\nRollers and brushes are very similar. They are short-range weapons that can fling ink and spread ink by rolling on the ground. Rollers can fling ink farther by flinging while jumping.\n"},{"text":"Splat Roller","color":"red"},{"text":"\nThe basic roller type.\n"},{"text":"Carbon Roller","color":"red"},{"text":"\nA weak but fast roller.\n"},{"text":"Dynamo Roller","color":"red"},{"text":"\nA strong but slow roller.\n"},{"text":"Flingza Roller","color":"red"},{"text":"\nA roller with a weak and fast ground fling, and a slow, long-range jump fling."}]
tellraw @s ["",{"text":"Inkbrush","color":"red"},{"text":"\nA very light roller-like weapon. Can move extremely quickly by rolling.\n"},{"text":"Octobrush","color":"red"},{"text":"\nA slightly heavier version of the Inkbrush. Doesn't roll as fast, but deals more damage."}]